summary: Some ideas for the gaming channel going forward
body:
Some ideas for the gaming channel going forward

I know Dan and Phil dont have to do any of this, these are just my suggestions.

1. Play more games to completion. I love the undertale playthrough because we got to take the entire game journey with Dan and Phil. Watching them play more games to the end would be more emotionally satisfying for me.

2. Upload less frequently. Maybe having a consistent schedule but with less uploads a month would mean they can play games because they are the games DNP want to play, instead of feeling obligated to find something. Plus it might take some of the pressure off.

DNP can do whatever they want. I just think these things could help.
